
Resolution for responsivity :

Add to your .css files

===========================
Little mobile devices
==========================

@media only screen and (max-width:764px) {
    html {
        
        /* background: yellow; */
    }

=============================
Big mobile devices
===========================


@media only screen and (min-device-width:765px ) and (max-device-width: 1023px){
    /*-------IPAD resolution 768px -------*/

================
Desktop
==========


@media only screen and (min-width:1024px) {
    /*-------IPAD PRO resolution 1024px and above -------*/
   
